companyName: PGIM ETF Trust – PGIM Corporate Bond 5-10 Year ETF
description: PGIM ETF Trust – PGIM Corporate Bond 5-10 Year ETF is an actively managed ETF that invests primarily in investment‐grade corporate bonds—issued by U.S. and non-U.S. issuers—with maturities between five and ten years. It uses top-down and bottom-up research, proprietary models, and risk management; aims to maintain portfolio duration within one year of the Bloomberg U.S. Corporate 5-10 Year Index.
